{"tid":950123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄺保羅聖誕文告   冀各界助青年珍惜生命","createTime":"2018-12-21T09:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T00:47:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd69bc77bda466791778c4a5ec40e64c50e25dd","tid":950123,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2018/12/21/2021367_693a66cc74e8ca49a65834e6d48d1b6c_320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.hkej.com%2Fhkej%2Fimages%2F2018%2F12%2F21%2F2021367_693a66cc74e8ca49a65834e6d48d1b6c_320.jpg&h=24d17882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港聖公會教省主教長鄺保羅大主教發表2018年聖誕文告稱，聖誕節不單止是普天同慶的日子，也是改變人類歷史和轉化人生命的重要時刻。上帝珍視、寵愛所有生命，不論膚色、種族、信仰，每一個人在他眼中都是寶貴的。可惜的是，很多人都領悟不到聖誕節的真諦，沒有重視生命的價值。<br />\n<br />\n他續稱，自殺不單止白白放棄了寶貴的生命，亦會對親人、師長、朋友帶來心靈困擾和難以彌補的傷害，他們會因此自責愧疚，不斷承受負面情緒和壓力的煎熬，甚至會意志消沉，如同行屍走肉一樣。自殺個案一宗亦都嫌多，所謂預防勝於治療，要改變這個情況，社會各界必須攜手合作，採取實質行動解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n鄺保羅指出，政府應該有決心，提供足夠資源支援志願機構和宗教團體，在不同領域，包括教育、社服、醫療以及社交平台，制訂解決問題的政策和展開計劃，協助老師、社工、家長學習如何與有需要的青少年對話和溝通，聆聽他們的心聲。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，政府亦應該認真檢討教育制度和學校課程，不應只着重學業成績和學生人數，要開展生命教育和心靈教育課程，促進青少年的全人發展，培養每一個人從小認識生命的意義，幫助他們思考，在生命面對順境和逆境的時候應有的正確態度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2021367/%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%96%87%E5%91%8A+%E5%86%80%E5%90%84%E7%95%8C%E5%8A%A9%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2021367%2F%25E9%2584%25BA%25E4%25BF%259D%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2581%2596%25E8%25AA%2595%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2591%258A%2B%25E5%2586%2580%25E5%2590%2584%25E7%2595%258C%25E5%258A%25A9%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%258F%258D%25E6%2583%259C%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD&d=3OQGOEmz9Ym3FKyzYyZMx6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=efbcd06a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2021367/%E9%84%BA%E4%BF%9D%E7%BE%85%E8%81%96%E8%AA%95%E6%96%87%E5%91%8A+%E5%86%80%E5%90%84%E7%95%8C%E5%8A%A9%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E7%8F%8D%E6%83%9C%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD</a>"},{"pid":"0fa8878f7dcac963faa301f25cb10f854802f428","tid":950123,"uid":201604,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"有咩值得珍惜？"},{"pid":"5b8013f4c79096f306fb7cb0478b7dc75295e70b","tid":950123,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/c0511ul4lo6_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fc0511ul4lo6_496_280%2F0&h=c086519f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d8c7958c01d4138ffcd2c985c0609e60e21460e","tid":950123,"uid":20867,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5b8013f4c79096f306fb7cb0478b7dc75295e70b","tid":950123,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/c0511ul4lo6_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fc0511ul4lo6_496_280%2F0&h=c086519f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kong-02_zjG2C_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkong-02_zjG2C_1200x0.png&h=b5964439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsdb.memehk.com/img/post/15265_%EF%BC%A1%EF%BC%B3%EF%BC%A4%EF%BC%A6%EF%BC%A1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsdb.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F15265_%25EF%25BC%25A1%25EF%25BC%25B3%25EF%25BC%25A4%25EF%25BC%25A6%25EF%25BC%25A1.jpg&h=71708eea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"653f3faf138793fb3857f1c602df731187b0e448","tid":950123,"uid":4285,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T09:48:14.000Z","msg":